-1837223642.text: "Recent studies have shown that in cells undergoing nutrient deprivation- or ceramide induced autophagy, JNK1 phosphorylates serine 70 on Bcl-2, promoting disruption of Bcl-2 and Beclin-1 complexes, and liberating Beclin-1 to promote autophagy [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR]."
